  <heading>REV (predicate)</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Reverse all elements in a predicate</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction reads all elements in the source predicate,
reverses the order of all the elements, and places
the result in the destination predicate.
This instruction is unpredicated.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
  </desc>
